main event: At approximately 0730 hours, the witness observed a disc-shaped object hovering over a field near his residence in Brookesville, Florida.
interesting points: The object was approximately 40-50 feet in diameter and appeared to be metallic in color.
The object was observed for approximately 10-15 minutes before it accelerated rapidly and disappeared from view.
The witness wished to remain anonymous.
No other witnesses were identified, and no photographs or recordings were provided.
The case was classified as unresolved due to the lack of additional evidence.
